{"tid":1105476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長短腳之戀】侏儒男成英國「最矮爸爸」 感動抱B不忘向高妹老婆示愛","createTime":"2019-04-14T02:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T03:04:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6e7d7afe9009dbf7545b807a605ec68a340e17","tid":1105476,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"真愛可跨越任何障礙，英國3呎7吋（約1.09米）高的侏儒藝人勒斯第德（James Lusted）與5呎7吋（約1.7米）高妹的愛情開花結果，二人在婚後兩年半誕下一名健康女嬰，「成為她的爸爸，令我感到前所未有的美妙，我們珍惜每一刻時光」，勒斯第德亦因而晉身全英「最矮爸爸」之一。<br />\n來自英國北威爾斯的勒斯第德（James Lusted）現年30歲，兩年前與比他細5歲的克羅伊（Chloe）結婚，當時克羅伊表明不介意孩子或會遺傳侏儒基因，希望誕下二人的愛情結晶，結果她今年終成功誕下女嬰，而勒斯第德亦順理成章成為全英國其中一名最矮爸爸。勒斯第德表示︰「抱着女兒在懷內絕對是我曾經歷過的最美好的兩件事之一。」他不忘補充「迎娶克羅伊就是另一個生命中最美好的日子」，言語間盡顯他對妻女的愛。<br />\n初出生的女兒奧莉維婭（Olivia Nevaeh）重8磅3安士，非常健康，出生後24小時可出院，沒有遺傳到可引致畸形性發育不良（Diastrophic Dysplasia）的基因，「奧莉維婭是完美的。沒有字詞可以形容我們對奧莉維婭的愛，我們都高興得很，從來沒有感到如此強烈的愛&hellip;&hellip;當護士將她交到我的雙臂，我唯一可以說的是，我願意為她們奉獻生命。」<br />\n勒斯第德透露，女兒比預產期遲了3天出生，分娩過程歷時7小時，整體而言太太懷孕的過程很順利，現在兩夫婦一起照顧女兒的生活也過得很愜意，「克羅伊餵哺她，她半夜會睡覺，清晨5時會醒來。我猜她之所以很放鬆，因為克羅伊和我都很悠閒，她會感應到的。」勒斯第德希望日後再添寶寶，但現在會先享受和奧莉維婭一起的時光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190413/large/1555136699_2ee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190413%2Flarge%2F1555136699_2ee9.jpg&h=aac750d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190413/large/1555136881_1bf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190413%2Flarge%2F1555136881_1bf7.jpg&h=d7812930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190414/59483644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59483644&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8v%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=e8b85aca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F59483644&h=a84ea747\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190414/59483644</a>"},{"pid":"19adea3d24646abd30b35c725c473e407bab8977","tid":1105476,"uid":42431,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"有遺傳病就咪撚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a664299dd94d18a7d1a6c6a2f974b56d4989f2a7","tid":1105476,"uid":96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"企係到已經可以幫佢老婆奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27592f9b7868e2b538314f7c03d286022351596c","tid":1105476,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a664299dd94d18a7d1a6c6a2f974b56d4989f2a7","tid":1105476,"uid":96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"企係到已經可以幫佢老婆奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"仲有乜野花式可以玩？<br />\n<br />\n我諗到條女可以著住大肚婆裙出街<br />\n<br />\n入面就係條矮佬屌西"},{"pid":"27a2477db4b8b20fecb912a2391c7917ae33d302","tid":1105476,"uid":33907,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"19adea3d24646abd30b35c725c473e407bab8977","tid":1105476,"uid":42431,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"有遺傳病就咪撚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"嗰啲真係要落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好仆街"},{"pid":"81386655a6cbf8ae5f446648a723316ebfdc9908","tid":1105476,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有遺傳病就咪撚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>嗰啲真係要落地獄<img src=\"/assets